text: I didn’t blow all my money on Squishmallows. Kinda sad I didn’t buy the entire store. Honestly, I didn’t really do much—maybe learned to budget. Still want to buy the whole Squishmallow wall.
text_uk: I didn’t spend all my money on Squishmallows. Bit gutted I didn’t buy the entire shop. Honestly, didn’t really do much—suppose I learnt how to budget. Still fancy buying the whole Squishmallow wall.
